Flow Diagram

Start
   ↓
Initialize w1, w2, b
   ↓
For each epoch
   ↓
Take input (x1, x2)
   ↓
Compute z = w1x1 + w2x2 + b
   ↓
Apply Step Function
   ↓
Predict y_hat
   ↓
Compute Error = y - y_hat
   ↓
Is Error ≠ 0 ?
   ↓               ↓
  Yes              No
   ↓               ↓
Update weights     Next input
   ↓
Next input
   ↓
All epochs done?
   ↓
Test on all inputs
   ↓
End
